01:15:21.660 --> 01:15:24.660
Deal with it, Dipwan! Take his phone!

01:15:24.660 --> 01:15:28.660
But Stu was too far gone to listen.

01:15:28.660 --> 01:15:31.660
Coming up next, the hardware store where

01:15:31.660 --> 01:15:36.030
we used to buy our weather stripping.

01:15:36.030 --> 01:15:38.030
Oh!

01:15:38.030 --> 01:15:40.030
Meanwhile, things at band practice

01:15:40.030 --> 01:15:42.030
