01:15:42.030 --> 01:15:44.030
Breathe deep, my squibs.

01:15:44.030 --> 01:15:46.030
Work those lungs!

01:15:46.030 --> 01:15:52.900
I'm telling you, Pete,

01:15:52.900 --> 01:15:54.900
Michael's wigged.

01:15:54.900 --> 01:15:56.900
His wedding thing has warped his brain.

01:15:56.900 --> 01:15:58.900
Michael says my duck feeder

01:15:58.900 --> 01:16:00.900
