01:16:00.900 --> 01:16:02.900
If I can't angle him in 16 degrees,

01:16:02.900 --> 01:16:04.900
I'm out of the band.

01:16:04.900 --> 01:16:07.900
This isn't why we joined up.

01:16:07.900 --> 01:16:09.900
Maybe we should talk to him.

01:16:09.900 --> 01:16:11.900
Count Ellen out.

01:16:11.900 --> 01:16:13.900
What?

01:16:13.900 --> 01:16:14.900
I mean, take a look for yourself.

01:16:14.900 --> 01:16:15.900
She's partners with James

01:16:15.900 --> 01:16:17.900
and Michael Jr. now.

01:16:17.900 --> 01:16:30.910
They're partners?

01:16:30.910 --> 01:16:32.910
Yeah, I meant to tell you,

01:16:32.910 --> 01:16:34.910
