01:16:34.910 --> 01:16:36.910
What?

01:16:36.910 --> 01:16:38.910
I couldn't believe it.

01:16:38.910 --> 01:16:40.910
Ellen and Michael Jr.?

01:16:40.910 --> 01:16:42.910
What could she possibly have in common

01:16:42.910 --> 01:16:44.910
