01:16:44.910 --> 01:16:52.100
Ellen, when I look at you,

01:16:52.100 --> 01:16:54.100
you know what I see?

01:16:54.100 --> 01:16:56.100
A dot.

01:16:56.100 --> 01:16:59.100
Oh, well, I've been under a lot of pressure lately.

01:16:59.100 --> 01:17:01.100
No, no.

01:17:01.100 --> 01:17:04.100
A dot inside.

01:17:04.100 --> 01:17:06.100
I don't like the rest of these clowns.

01:17:06.100 --> 01:17:08.100
You could be a champion.

01:17:08.100 --> 01:17:13.620
Let me help you.

01:17:13.620 --> 01:17:16.620
Be the dot you were always meant to be.

01:17:16.620 --> 01:17:18.620
He helped her, all right.

01:17:18.620 --> 01:17:20.620
As the days passed,

01:17:20.620 --> 01:17:22.620
she became more and more consumed

01:17:22.620 --> 01:17:25.620
with achieving a state of total dot-osity.

01:17:25.620 --> 01:17:27.620
I am a dot.

01:17:27.620 --> 01:17:29.620
I am a dot.

01:17:29.620 --> 01:17:31.620
I am a dot.

01:17:31.620 --> 01:17:33.620
I am a dot.

01:17:33.620 --> 01:17:35.620
I am a dot.

01:17:35.620 --> 01:17:37.620
Then he set out to forge a psychic brain meld

01:17:37.620 --> 01:17:39.620
so they could stay perfectly in step

01:17:39.620 --> 01:17:41.620
and telepathically bridge the gap

01:17:41.620 --> 01:17:43.620
between the dot and the rest of the eye.

01:17:43.620 --> 01:17:45.620
Hi.

01:17:45.620 --> 01:17:49.190
Hi, Pete.

01:17:49.190 --> 01:17:51.190
