01:18:20.410 --> 01:18:22.410
I had seen enough.

01:18:22.410 --> 01:18:25.410
I wanted to remind Ellen what band was supposed to be

01:18:25.410 --> 01:18:31.380
and get her away from James Markle Jr.

01:18:31.380 --> 01:18:34.380
My plan wasn't based on the Crimean War or anything,

01:18:34.380 --> 01:18:36.380
