01:19:06.600 --> 01:19:08.600
Sure enough.

01:19:08.600 --> 01:19:10.600
Music of the God!

01:19:10.600 --> 01:19:13.600
I'm lying to him, George Clinton.

01:19:13.600 --> 01:19:21.460
By the time arty began dancing the voodoo crispy,

01:19:21.460 --> 01:19:27.280
Markle's spell was broken.

01:19:27.280 --> 01:19:29.280
When I saw Ellen laugh,

01:19:29.280 --> 01:19:32.280
I knew everything was going to be alright.

01:19:32.280 --> 01:19:35.280
How was I to know it wouldn't last?

01:19:35.280 --> 01:19:38.280
As arty launched into the diesel jerk,

01:19:38.280 --> 01:19:41.280
Markle was busy formulating a diabolical scheme

01:19:41.280 --> 01:19:44.280
