01:28:23.180 --> 01:28:34.400
Yes.

01:28:34.400 --> 01:28:35.400
I didn't know it then,

01:28:35.400 --> 01:28:38.400
but as I marched towards the rest of my lonely life,

01:28:38.400 --> 01:28:41.400
another love-lorn man was hurtling towards the field

01:28:41.400 --> 01:28:44.400
