01:29:10.270 --> 01:29:29.650
A uniform?

01:29:29.650 --> 01:29:31.650
Did I tell you about the only girl

01:29:31.650 --> 01:29:35.920
who could ever share my life?

01:29:35.920 --> 01:29:40.780
Well, let me tell you about Driver Sally Knorp.

01:29:40.780 --> 01:29:41.780
Maybe somewhere in America.

01:30:01.650 --> 01:30:03.650
When love comes,

01:30:03.650 --> 01:30:05.650
you better pull over to the side of the road

01:30:05.650 --> 01:30:07.650
and open your door

01:30:07.650 --> 01:30:09.650
because nothing in this world matters more.

01:30:09.650 --> 01:30:41.240
Knorp?

01:30:41.240 --> 01:31:40.040
Ten seconds!

01:31:40.040 --> 01:31:43.040
Seeing Driver Stu and Driver Sally,

01:31:43.040 --> 01:31:45.040
