01:31:48.040 --> 01:31:58.080
Somehow, I had to show Ellen how I felt.

01:31:58.080 --> 01:32:00.080
It was the riskiest move of my life,

01:32:00.080 --> 01:32:06.300
but I had to do it.

01:32:06.300 --> 01:32:08.300
The band was so well-trained,

01:32:08.300 --> 01:32:09.300
