01:32:12.300 --> 01:32:26.500
I tried to remember our science film,

01:32:26.500 --> 01:32:29.500
so I could recreate the chain reaction we saw.

01:32:40.690 --> 01:32:44.440
Ladies and gentlemen,

01:32:44.440 --> 01:32:47.440
the fighting squids have just made a formation

01:32:47.440 --> 01:32:50.440
never before attempted on any football field.

01:32:50.440 --> 01:32:52.440
It looks like...

01:32:52.440 --> 01:32:54.440
the song!

01:32:54.440 --> 01:32:57.440
Luke, somebody pinch me.

01:32:57.440 --> 01:32:59.440
I believe they're ready to attempt

01:32:59.440 --> 01:33:01.440
a thermonuclear fusion

01:33:01.440 --> 01:33:04.440
of force that powers the stones.

